{"tid":532393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[曾志偉] 將藍潔瑛2013年訪問片段加速120%","createTime":"2018-01-17T20:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T09:09:43.000Z","uid":15696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"206cc8598fa1b0de87802c7835683258233a7b75","tid":532393,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T20:09:32.000Z","msg":"我見好多人話段片之前係男聲 今次係女聲<br />\n<br />\n不過其實明眼人都聽到把聲只不過係減左速？<br />\n<br />\n將2013年段片把男聲加速120%<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/ohhhhnnnnoo/test\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fohhhhnnnnoo%2Ftest&d=rf2Rgc6hJaqUPXdShLT%2BcGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=dce4b8be\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/ohhhhnnnnoo/test</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bo9XMtVs1Mw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBo9XMtVs1Mw&d=rf2Rgc6hJaqUPXdShLT%2BcGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=9888de01\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bo9XMtVs1Mw</a><br />\n<br />\n咁即係有人係2013年已經偽造定段片？<br />\n<br />\n定係偽造同一把聲插返把聲入去？ <br />\n<br />\n我想知點做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b1b5f09e72c86c52d89b37b55ab301df7534d09","tid":532393,"uid":15696,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T20:14:50.000Z","msg":"首先在2013年發布的視頻裡，畫外的提問者是男聲，而這一次則變為了女聲，提問者的發言雖大體相同，但有少許出入，並不會是簡單的聲音處理，而是<strong>重新配音</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n重新配音?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ce0339b46531f7f108266f58c4aebd996628a6","tid":532393,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T22:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n直播同藍潔瑛對質咪得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e84c43bea1070da930b4e3e0bb373ef301a3a0de","tid":532393,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T22:12:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27659158a0872037ab2f2d5a491d73fd501d8761","tid":532393,"uid":120786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T22:26:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果呢個時候藍出黎指證會點?</blockquote><br />\n會死"},{"pid":"27dc8c8fbdac76741b8fe8fc0e0b203d28194fbd","tid":532393,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T22:46:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55600bf579e83686e85e7de072d1bc6392e12b8e","tid":532393,"uid":48796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"27dc8c8fbdac76741b8fe8fc0e0b203d28194fbd","tid":532393,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27659158a0872037ab2f2d5a491d73fd501d8761","tid":532393,"uid":120786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T22:26:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果呢個時候藍出黎指證會點?</blockquote><br />\n會死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T22:46:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T00:10:00.000Z","msg":"呢個時候有乜冬瓜豆腐, 米奇真係水洗都唔清 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba1617a4edbbdf0a7b8b028b35ba46c4969a8a7","tid":532393,"uid":101968,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T00:35:47.000Z","msg":"曼德拉效應"},{"pid":"bbd316b0c51f4d4d1cdf51364e888ea9002db7eb","tid":532393,"uid":33077,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T02:54:44.000Z","msg":"藍潔瑛都神智不清 d人又會話未必可信啦<br />\n到時咪又係搞到佢激動<br />\n都大半世人<br />\n希望傳媒唔好主動搞佢<br />\n除非佢自己肯出黎講野"},{"pid":"f434e1c64eb3fc6c29093359090229cdcb21552c","tid":532393,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T05:23:41.000Z","msg":"明明同一把聲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"342ac5ec1ffb3402bb3619af021c0bbfbe